# .npmrc is local-only: node-linker=hoisted is required for the dev tunnel
# prod-build workflow (see CLAUDE.md "Dev Tunnel") to work around a Rollup
# pnpm-symlink resolution bug. Cloudflare Pages must NOT see this file -
# its build pipeline already handles pnpm symlinks correctly with the
# default layout, and forcing hoisted there broke CF Pages builds.
